                    <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length" data-sr="vF 0.6">Looking at the&nbsp;<br />bigger picture</h2>
                    <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length" data-sr="vF 0">We conducted interviews with the client&rsqu;s internal teams and provided recommendations on workflow involving UX designers, product managers, engineers, and marketing reps.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-block half float-right full-height">
                    <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/snagajob/laptop-website.jpg" />
